sequenceDiagram
    participant CI as CI/CD Runner<br/>(Konflux Tekton)
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>(Go CLI)
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Reg as Red Hat Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>(Build Context)
    participant Docker as Dockerfile.konflux<br/>(Image Build)
    participant Operator as rhods-operator
    participant Container as Data Container<br/>(ubi9-minimal)
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over CI,FS: Flow 1: Model Metadata Extraction Pipeline (Build-Time)
        CI->>Extractor: Execute model-extractor binary
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections<br/>GET /api/users/RedHatAI/collections<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>Extractor: Collection metadata
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{id}<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>Extractor: Model details
        Extractor->>HF: GET /{model}/raw/main/README.md<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>Extractor: README / YAML frontmatter
        Extractor->>Reg: GET OCI manifests + layer blobs<br/>Auth: Anonymous<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Reg-->>Extractor: Model cards, image configs
        Extractor->>FS: Write models-catalog.yaml<br/>Write metadata files
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Extractor,FS: Flow 3: MCP Server Catalog Generation (Build-Time)
        Extractor->>FS: Read MCP index YAML<br/>Read MCP input YAML files
        Extractor->>Reg: GET OCI manifests<br/>(MCP server images)<br/>Auth: Docker config<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Reg-->>Extractor: Architectures, timestamps
        Extractor->>FS: Write *-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Docker,Dashboard: Flow 2: Model Catalog Consumption (Runtime)
        FS->>Docker: COPY data/*.yaml → /app/data/
        Docker->>Container: Build minimal image<br/>(ubi9-minimal + YAML files only)
        Operator->>Reg: Pull odh-model-metadata-collection image<br/>Auth: Image pull secret<br/>HTTPS/443
        Operator->>Container: Deploy as init container/sidecar
        Container->>Dashboard: Volume mount /app/data/*.yaml<br/>(Filesystem read, no network)
    end
